snippet.title: ACA NEOGEO MUTATION NATION
snippet.description:
MUTATION NATION is an action game released by SNK in 1992. 
Humans turned into mutants by the hands of a genius biologist have gone on a rampage. To save their hometown, 
two youths rise up to resist. Battle with courage using full action combos along with 6 special moves.

©SNK CORPORATION ALL RIGHTS RESERVED.
